# Dashboard Pattern

## Composition (server-first)

Page header → optional hero/summary → KPI grid → primary widgets/feeds → secondary panels.

## Rules

- Scope KPIs to active org/store/workspace
- Load data on the server when using Next App Router
- Every widget owns loading/empty/error — no blank boxes
- Quick actions link to real workflows, not placeholders
- No fake metrics. If data is missing, show empty state.

## Density

Ops dashboards prioritize scannability and action. Avoid marketing-style hero clutter.
